::Triggerhappy::

      Triggerhappy pauses for a moment, then shakes Motormaster's hand.

      "I was scrapped along time ago by our Autobot enemies.  My parts were
stored away on a distant planet, and a couple centuries ago, the people on
that planet restored me, and sent me to Earth in a pod, as safe from danger
as anything," He said.

      "Well, is there any Autobots in the perimeter that need a lesson?" He
said, not knowing about the new days.
